ShinyCMS TODO
=============

A list of features and functionality that I'd like to add to ShinyCMS in the 
future (short or long term).


* User area
	* OpenID integration

* CMS Pages
	* Add/remove templates
	* Menus
	* Sections
	* Screenshot of page layout on edit page, changing with template selection
	* Add/edit could read in the page_element names from the template
	* Per-page/section edit/admin ACLs

* Forms
	* Contact form

* Shop
	* Catalogue
		* Storefront (default shop page - recent offers? something)
	* Basket
		* Wishlist
	* Checkout
		* Credit card payment processing
			* Worldpay
			* CCBill
			* etc

* Galleries
	* Batch uploads
	* Tagging
	
* Blogs
	* Posts
		* Create new post (probably needs fixing after blog_post primary key change)
		* Edit post (ditto)
		* Limit recent posts list to 'last 10', 'last 20', etc
		* Chronological / calendar-based view
		* Search
	* Comments
		* Add comment
		* Edit comment (?)
		* OpenID
	* Trackbacks
	* Pings

* Forums

